des: "Pudding shots are not just for college."
ins: Stir milk, schnapps, Irish cream liqueur, vodka, and coffee-flavored liqueur together in a bowl. Add pudding mix and blend thoroughly. Spoon into disposable shot cups and refrigerate until chilled, at least 30 minutes.
